    "This capability bridges the gap between domain experts without coding expertise and software development, enabling more intuitive and collaborative software-design processes.In particular, LLM may also be trained with the repository of a simulation code, including documentation, the code itself, as well as code examples.",
    "However, in order to generate a simulation model from natural language, besides general NLP capabilities, the LLM also requires some mechanical-engineering knowledge such as geometry, kinematics, statics or dynamics.",
    "Therefore, particular training of LLM solely with the documentation of a simulation code could be insufficient.",
    "The LLaMA modelLLaMA-2, introduced in July 2023 as a collaboration between Meta AI and Microsoft, represents a further refinement of LLaMA-1, often denoted as LLaMA.",
    "4 It was launched in three model sizes: 7B, 13B, and 70B parameters."
